'''阿薩‧拉斯金'''（{{Lang-en|'''Aza Raskin'''}}，{{bd|1984年|}}）是[[美國|美國]]的[[設計|設計]][[專家|專家]]<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.oneopensource.it/01/09/2008/interview-aza-raskin-head-of-user-experience-for-mozilla-labs/ | title=Interview with Aza Raskin, Head of User Experience for Mozilla Labs | work=oneopensource | first=Matteo | last=Campofiorito | date=September 1, 2008 | accessdate=2009-03-06 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110722044849/http://www.oneopensource.it/01/09/2008/interview-aza-raskin-head-of-user-experience-for-mozilla-labs/ | archivedate=2011-07-22}}</ref> 及[[用戶界面|介面]][[大師|大師]]。<ref>{{cite news| url=http://news.cnet.com/8301-17939_109-10191921-2.html| title=Firefox, too, revamping new-tab behavior | first=Stephen | last=Shankland | work=CNET News | date=March 8, 2009 | accessdate=2009-03-10}}</ref> 他同時也是知名[[人機界面|人機界面]]專家[[傑夫·拉斯金|傑夫·拉斯金]]之子。

==傳記==
拉斯金在10歲時於[[交互專業學會|人機互動學會]][[舊金山|舊金山]]分會發表人生第一次的[[用戶界面|使用者界面]]演說<ref>{{cite conference | first=Jef | last=Raskin | coauthors=Aza Raskin|authorlink=Jef Raskin | title=The Interface Paradox | url=http://www.baychi.org/calendar/19940913/ | booktitle=BayCHI Monthly Program | date=September 13, 1994 | accessdate=2009-03-06}}</ref>。20歲時，他便開始於國外發表演說<ref>{{cite conference | first = Aza | last = Raskin | title = The Failure of Applications | booktitle = EuroPython 2004 | location = [[Gothenburg|Gothenburg]], [[Sweden|Sweden]] | date = 2004 | url = http://europython-develop.zope.nl/conferences/epc2004/info/talks/applications/jacob02 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080309010633/http://europython-develop.zope.nl/conferences/epc2004/info/talks/applications/jacob02 | archivedate = 2008-03-09 }}</ref>。他擁有[[芝加哥大學|芝加哥大學]][[數學|數學]]及[[物理學|物理學]]的學士學位<ref name="blog">{{cite web | last=Raskin | first=Aza | url=http://www.azarask.in/blog/ | title=Aza's Thoughts - About me | accessdate=2009-03-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090228225729/http://www.azarask.in/blog/ | archive-date=2009-02-28 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>，並短暫攻讀[[加州理工學院|加州理工學院]]物理博士學位，繼續他曾在芝加哥大學和[[東京大學|東京大學]]參與的[[暗物質|暗物質]]研究{{fact|date=September 2008}}。拉斯金未完成[[中學|初中]]、[[中學|高中]]及[[研究所|研究所]]學業，芝加哥大學是他唯一獲得學位的學校{{fact|date=September 2008}}。

2004年，拉斯金與其父傑夫‧拉斯金在拉斯金人機介面中心一同發展新式使用介面[[Archy|Archy]]<ref>{{cite news | last=McCarthy | first=Jack | date=February 28, 2005 | url=http://weblog.infoworld.com/techwatch/archives/001138.html | title=Mac creator Jef Raskin dies of cancer | work=InfoWorld | accessdate=2008-03-06 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20050303064851/http://weblog.infoworld.com/techwatch/archives/001138.html | archivedate=2005-03-03}}</ref>。次年，他開設[[Humanized|Humanized]]公司，持續進行Archy的開發工作。在Humanized，他開發了以語言為基礎、服務導向的軟體[[Enso_(電腦軟體)|Enso]]。

2008年1月，拉斯金及其他Humanized公司成員加入[[Mozilla公司|Mozilla公司]]<ref>{{ cite news | last=Raskin | first=Aza | url=http://humanized.com/weblog/2008/01/16/joining-mozilla/ | title=Joining Mozilla | publisher=Humanized | date=January 16, 2008 | accessdate=2009-03-06 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080120152125/http://www.humanized.com/weblog/2008/01/16/joining-mozilla | archivedate=2008-01-20}}</ref>，拉斯金成為[[Mozilla|Mozilla Labs]]專案的使用體驗負責人<ref name="blog" />，並參與諸如[[Ubiquity|Ubiquity]]<ref>{{cite news | last=Raskin | first=Aza | url=http://labs.mozilla.com/2008/08/introducing-ubiquity/ | title=Introducing Ubiquity | publisher=[[Mozilla_Labs|Mozilla Labs]] | date=August 26, 2008 | accessdate=2009-03-06 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090308032333/http://labs.mozilla.com/2008/08/introducing-ubiquity/ | archivedate=2009-03-08}}</ref>與[[Firefox行動版|Firefox行動版]]等專案<ref>{{cite news | first=Erick | last=Schonfeld | url=http://www.techcrunch.com/2008/06/11/zoom-pan-throw-a-peek-at-what-firefox-mobile-could-be/ | title=Zoom, Pan, Throw: A Peek At What Firefox Mobile Could Be | publisher=[[TechCrunch|TechCrunch]] | date=June 11, 2008 | accessdate=2009-03-06}}</ref>。

拉斯金創立了兩間公司，包括[[音樂|音樂]]搜尋工具[[Songza|Songza]]及銷售紙製家具的[[Bloxes|Bloxes]]，是名成功的企業家<ref>{{cite news | url=http://news.cnet.com/8301-11128_3-9888750-54.html | title=Cardboard key to a 'green' office space | last=Wenzel | first=Elsa | date=March 7, 2008 | work=CNET News | accessdate=2009-03-06}}</ref>。其中Songza已於2008年底被[[Amazon.com|亞馬遜]]投資的[[艾米街|艾米街]]收購<ref>{{cite news |url=http://techcrunch.com/2009/04/08/news-flash-amie-street-swallowed-songza-six-months-ago/ |title=News Flash: Amie Street Swallowed Songza Six Months Ago |publisher=[[TechCrunch|TechCrunch]] |date=Apr 8, 2009}}</ref>。他也有一些規模較小的專案，如以[[形式文法|規範語法]]生成[[藝術|藝術]]作品的[[演算油墨|演算油墨]]專案<ref>{{cite web |url=http://azarask.in/projects/algorithm-ink/ |title=Algorithm Ink |publisher=Aza Raskin |access-date=2009-09-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080812221420/http://azarask.in/projects/algorithm-ink/ |archive-date=2008-08-12 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2010年，拉斯金發現了新型態的[[網絡釣魚|網絡釣魚]]手法，稱為標籤綁架（Tabnabbing），當使用者連上嵌有惡意程式的網頁時，在使用者閒置一段時間後，該惡意網頁分頁及內容會悄悄地偽裝成網路服務，誘導使用者輸入帳號和密碼<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.azarask.in/blog/post/a-new-type-of-phishing-attack/ |title=Tabnabbing: A New Type of Phishing Attack |publisher=Aza Raskin |access-date=2010-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120217193155/http://www.azarask.in/blog/post/a-new-type-of-phishing-attack/ |archive-date=2012-02-17 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

2010年12月15日，拉斯金離開Mozilla公司，創立Massive Health健康諮詢公司<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.azarask.in/blog/post/leaving-mozilla|title=Leaving Mozilla, Starting Massive Health|author=Aza Raskin|access-date=2014-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150206031148/http://www.azarask.in/blog/post/leaving-mozilla/|archive-date=2015-02-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

